For each angle two runs were measured, with spin 'up'
and 'down', respectively. For each peak in the
spectrum, and at each angle, both the differential
cross section and the analyzing power were determined.
The reaction products were
analyzed at eleven angles between 6. and 35. degr.with
the Munich Q3D spectrograph, and then detected in a
1.8 m long focal plane detector consisted of a
multiwire detector, two single wire detectors and
plastic scintillator in coincidence.
